('NEWS0000641', '2026-01-04 02:07:19.757', 'Bloomberg', 'Editorial Board', 'Federal Reserve Signals Potential Rate Cut', 'The Federal Reserve indicated today that it may consider cutting interest rates in the coming months if inflation continues to moderate. In prepared remarks, Fed Chair emphasized that the central bank remains data-dependent but acknowledged recent progress on price stability. Treasury yields fell sharply on the news, with the 10-year note dropping 15 basis points. Equity markets rallied broadly as investors priced in a more accommodative monetary policy stance.', 'Fed signals potential rate cuts; Treasury yields fall sharply', 'https://financial-news.example.com/article/641', 'JPM,BAC,GS,C', 'Financials', 'MARKET_WRAP', '0.7100', 'POSITIVE', '0.6100', '2026-02-17 14:27:19.757'),
