('NEWS0000679', '2026-01-01 10:47:19.757', 'The Motley Fool', 'David Wilson', 'Market Wrap: Stocks Close Mixed on Economic Data', 'Markets closed mixed today as investors digested a busy day of economic data and corporate earnings. The S&P 500 edged higher by 0.2% while the Dow Jones Industrial Average declined 0.1%. Small cap stocks outperformed with the Russell 2000 gaining 0.8%. Trading volume was in line with recent averages. Investors continue to monitor developments in trade negotiations and central bank policy ahead of next weeks key inflation report.', 'Mixed close: S&P +0.2%, Dow -0.1%; light volume', 'https://financial-news.example.com/article/679', 'SPY,QQQ,DIA', 'Broad Market', 'ANALYSIS', '0.2900', 'NEUTRAL', '0.9900', '2026-02-17 14:27:19.757'),
