('NEWS0001305', '2025-11-18 23:27:19.757', 'MarketWatch', 'John Smith', 'Cryptocurrency Markets Experience Volatility', 'Cryptocurrency markets experienced significant volatility today as Bitcoin briefly dropped below $40,000 before recovering to trade near $42,000. The selloff was attributed to regulatory concerns and profit-taking following the recent rally. Ethereum and other major altcoins followed a similar pattern. Despite the turbulence, crypto proponents maintain a bullish long-term outlook citing institutional adoption and upcoming technical upgrades.', 'Crypto volatility: Bitcoin drops below $40K before recovering', 'https://financial-news.example.com/article/1305', 'JPM,BAC,GS,C', 'Financials', 'ECONOMIC_DATA', '0.0500', 'NEUTRAL', '0.8500', '2026-02-17 14:27:19.757'),
