('NEWS0002785', '2025-08-08 05:47:19.757', 'MarketWatch', 'Analysis Team', 'Cryptocurrency Markets Experience Volatility', 'Cryptocurrency markets experienced significant volatility today as Bitcoin briefly dropped below $40,000 before recovering to trade near $42,000. The selloff was attributed to regulatory concerns and profit-taking following the recent rally. Ethereum and other major altcoins followed a similar pattern. Despite the turbulence, crypto proponents maintain a bullish long-term outlook citing institutional adoption and upcoming technical upgrades.', 'Crypto volatility: Bitcoin drops below $40K before recovering', 'https://financial-news.example.com/article/2785', 'JPM,BAC,GS,C', 'Financials', 'ANALYSIS', '0.0500', 'NEUTRAL', '0.8500', '2026-02-17 14:27:19.757'),
('NEWS0002786', '2025-08-08 04:07:19.757', 'Barrons', 'Editorial Board', 'Supply Chain Concerns Weigh on Industrial Stocks', 'Industrial stocks came under pressure today as ongoing supply chain disruptions continued to impact manufacturing operations. Several major companies lowered their full-year guidance citing logistics challenges and component shortages. The Industrial Select Sector SPDR fund declined 1.8% on the session. Supply chain experts suggest normalization could take another 6-12 months, particularly in sectors reliant on Asian suppliers.', 'Industrial stocks fall on supply chain guidance cuts', 'https://financial-news.example.com/article/2786', 'XOM,CVX,COP', 'Energy', 'EARNINGS', '-0.1400', 'NEGATIVE', '0.8600', '2026-02-17 14:27:19.757'),
