('NEWS0002997', '2025-07-24 12:27:19.757', 'Yahoo Finance', 'Editorial Board', 'Activist Investor Takes Stake in Major Corporation', 'The banking sector faced increased scrutiny today as regulators announced plans for enhanced oversight of large financial institutions. New proposed rules would require banks to hold additional capital reserves and strengthen risk management practices. Bank stocks declined on average 2% as investors assessed the potential impact on profitability. Industry groups have signaled they will provide feedback during the public comment period.', 'Banks decline as regulators propose stricter capital rules', 'https://financial-news.example.com/article/2997', 'BTC,ETH', 'Crypto', 'ECONOMIC_DATA', '-0.0800', 'NEGATIVE', '0.9700', '2026-02-17 14:27:19.757'),
('NEWS0002998', '2025-07-24 10:47:19.757', 'Seeking Alpha', 'Editorial Board', 'Global Trade Tensions Escalate', 'Consumer confidence surged to its highest level in two years according to the latest survey data released today. The index rose to 115.3 from 108.7 in the prior month, well above consensus estimates. Respondents cited improved job market conditions and moderating inflation as key factors boosting sentiment. The strong reading bodes well for consumer spending heading into the important holiday shopping season.', 'Consumer confidence hits 2-year high at 115.3', 'https://financial-news.example.com/article/2998', 'CAT,DE,HON,MMM', 'Industrials', 'FEATURE', '0.9300', 'POSITIVE', '0.9800', '2026-02-17 14:27:19.757'),
('NEWS0002999', '2025-07-24 09:07:19.757', 'The Motley Fool', 'Editorial Board', 'Market Wrap: Stocks Close Mixed on Economic Data', 'Markets closed mixed today as investors digested a busy day of economic data and corporate earnings. The S&P 500 edged higher by 0.2% while the Dow Jones Industrial Average declined 0.1%. Small cap stocks outperformed with the Russell 2000 gaining 0.8%. Trading volume was in line with recent averages. Investors continue to monitor developments in trade negotiations and central bank policy ahead of next weeks key inflation report.', 'Mixed close: S&P +0.2%, Dow -0.1%; light volume', 'https://financial-news.example.com/article/2999', 'SPY,QQQ,DIA', 'Broad Market', 'MARKET_WRAP', '0.3900', 'NEUTRAL', '0.9900', '2026-02-17 14:27:19.757');